sources.title: The Kid's Last Ride (1941) THE RANGE BUSTERS
sources.description:
Stars: Ray Corrigan, John 'Dusty' King, Max Terhune
 Director: S. Roy Luby

 Harmon forces Jimmy to reveal the location of some hidden money. When Harmon's men go after the money, the Range Busters break up the attempted robbery. For his next move, Harmon lays a trap for Crash.

sources.title: The Kid's Last Ride (1941) Ray 'Crash' Corrigan | Full Length Western
sources.description:
The Range Busters are hired as lawmen by the notorious Breeden Brothers, two-thirds of trio of three ruthless outlaws now disguised and renamed as solid citizens.

Director: S. Roy Luby
Writers: Earle Snell, Earle Snell 
Stars: Ray 'Crash' Corrigan, John 'Dusty' King, Max Terhune
Genres: Western
